_sText:
An aim-able people cannon. Have fun. You cant see the controls in the screen shot and I'm much too lazy to make a better one...just download it and check it out.

Just some fun. I may include this in a future surf map. The map is by no means perfect, just meant to demonstrate the cannon.

If you know how I can make people accelerate faster or have an idea for the cannons use, please leave a message.
